{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, there is an increase in services equipped with features that enhance accessibility, such as read-aloud functions, voice input, and subtitles.With the diversification of services, there is a growing expectation for personalized service adaptations [19].",
    "Personalized service adaptation is a technology that recommends and provides services tailored to individual preferences.",
    "For instance, the goals of smart home services vary significantly depending on lifestyle, ranging from comfort, health, environmental protection, and cost-saving to safety.",
    "Even in the case of automatic air conditioning adjustment, individual preferences can vary widely, such as keeping the room constantly cool, reducing noise at night, maintaining a temperature that prevents colds, avoiding dryness, being environmentally friendly, minimizing electricity costs, or ensuring long-term durability without breakdowns.",
    "Personalized adaptation promises not only to improve user satisfaction and the consequent profits but also to distribute limited resources, such as computing assets and electricity, effectively to the appropriate users."
  ]
}